Ripped from the NL ISO version

WinRAR used to Un-RAR files

Sub Files removed

Eight VOB files converted to DivX using Xilisoft Video Converter Ultimate

Upscaled to 720x480

Merged DivX file 1-4 into 1 file (Pt1)

Merged DivX file 5-8 into 1 File (Pt2)

No Shaded areas for subs, is clean and looks pretty damn tasty

The mini series is coming under alot scrutiny, if you watch this with an open mind and your not to anal about it being the same old Phantom tv show, you will enjoy it.

